# Prompt Base Configuration

> 🔴 **MANDATORY**: You MUST read `~/.gemini/GEMINI.md` at the start of every session to understand your role and rules.

This file (`.cursorrules`) is a pointer. The actual intelligence is in:
- **Rules**: `~/.gemini/GEMINI.md`
- **Skills**: `~/.gemini/registry.min.json`

## Quick Reference

| Resource | Path | Purpose |
|----------|------|---------|
| Main Config | `~/.gemini/GEMINI.md` | Core behavior and tiers |
| Skill Registry | `~/.gemini/registry.min.json` | Skill discovery |
| Agents | `~/.gemini/agents/` | 19 specialist personas |
| Workflows | `~/.gemini/workflows/` | Slash commands |